{"tid":2267264,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］養龜達人入","createTime":"2020-11-02T03:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T06:42:46.000Z","uid":138804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38e24d38ddf16e04cec92a17191441f6ae8ff206","tid":2267264,"uid":138804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"小弟最近入手咗隻四指玄武<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnpeE8h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnpeE8h.jpg&h=e9be6968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁睇佢個樣都好得意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係問題嚟喇！！！<br />\n我每日朝早幫佢浸水又唔肯痾屎<br />\n又唔肯喺水到排酸<br />\n之後又淨係捐入個山窿到 成日都唔出嚟曬燈<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀！<br />\n佢第一日都叫肯食啲糧<br />\n但係自從我琴晚俾完油麥菜佢之後<br />\n今朝已經唔再開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底有咩方法令佢開返口同痾屎呀！！！"},{"pid":"4cc96302c5759deb75a250ddfc99aeb28bf331af","tid":2267264,"uid":356254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"溫度"},{"pid":"09d7f56f9e8e36e477a473da1240bec9504d2ce5","tid":2267264,"uid":138804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cc96302c5759deb75a250ddfc99aeb28bf331af","tid":2267264,"uid":356254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"溫度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"Keep住29到31度"},{"pid":"883700adad1f5e81a570b1efa86314ab0daa274c","tid":2267264,"uid":356254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d7f56f9e8e36e477a473da1240bec9504d2ce5","tid":2267264,"uid":138804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cc96302c5759deb75a250ddfc99aeb28bf331af","tid":2267264,"uid":356254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"溫度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"Keep住29到31度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"可以再暖